    <stitle>HYDRO-MAX II BRAKE MONITOR SYSTEM - SWITCH ADJUSTMENT - 2037331C1</stitle>
    <svcsection/>
    <svcproc svcproctype="adjust" graphiccount="0">
        <title>2037331C1</title>
        <para>The 2037331C1 push button switch is not adjustable, and a good switch will function properly if the pedal
            stop is in adjustment. The pedal stop bolt is properly adjusted when it is 1/4 turn away from the brake
            pedal arm.
        </para>
    </svcproc>
